# NY Benchmark - LLM Context

Part of the New York Benchmarking Project.
Tagline: Civic reform through benchmarking.

## What This Is

NY Benchmark is a Rails application for collecting, verifying, and benchmarking financial data from New York State local governments.

This is the data application. The project blog is at https://nybenchmark.org

